history.content:
128 labs are very well-defined and scoped, so it’s possible to consistently finish in less than 3 hours if you’ve prepared adequately.

The hardware in 106A is considerably more advanced, so labs are less reliable or it’s easier to have a failure in understanding. The variance in lab duration is higher (some weeks easily <3 hours, others needed to be made up).
